  "about": "Tokita Ohma, also known as The Asura, is a man who loves to fight. He entered into the Kengan Association, fighting for the Nogi Group. During the Kengan Annihilation Tournament, Ohma fought for Yamashita Trading Co. with Yamashita Kazuo as his employer. Throughout the Kengan Annihilation Tournament he became more level headed and less cocky.\n\nHe is one of the chosen 13 fighters for Kengan side for the Kengan vs Purgatory tournament.",
